Welcome back to Blue Valley, the small town in Nebraska protected by a new generation of the JSA led proudly by Courtney Whitmore aka Stargirl! With her team in tow and S.T.R.I.P.E. by her side, they stand united, ready to take on any threat the former ISA can produce. This time, things get bleak when the literal spirit of evil in the form of the Angel of Vengeance Eclipso sets his sights on the unknowing citizens of. Join us as we discuss another stellar season of Stargirl, talk about stakes in comic book media, and what separates this show from others in the comic book TV pantheon.

